desc: The WFH Desk is an ergonomic, highly-acclaimed home desk that's also modular. Crafted from premium birchwood ply right here in NZ, you can select modules and accessories to add on to the WFH Desk to create your ideal home workstation. Or simply choose a setup from one of our pre-selected desk and accessory bundles.
